cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GT, cs.MA, cs.RO 

This paper focuses on reinforcement learning and its application to a specific multi-agent benchmark game, Pommerman. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses deep reinforcement learning, which suggests that cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category. The paper also mentions game theory and multi-agent systems, which could fall under cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems), respectively. Finally, the paper proposes a new framework that integrates Monte Carlo tree search, which could fall under cs.RO (Robotics).
